":1131704,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"d女一定好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f5066d8e575b82babc33f97d13c30df1ab8351","tid":1131704,"uid":147376,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1718177-中國-恢復邦交+岡比亞總統首訪華\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1718177-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E9%82%A6%E4%BA%A4%2B%E5%B2%A1%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E9%A6%96%E8%A8%AA%E8%8F%AF&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=4d3b7367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F1718177-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E9%82%A6%E4%BA%A4%2B%E5%B2%A1%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E9%A6%96%E8%A8%AA%E8%8F%AF&h=88df9c05\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1718177-中國-恢復邦交+岡比亞總統首訪華</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-12-21<br />\n<br />\n非洲國家岡比亞與台灣斷交之後，去年三月與中國大陸復交，總統巴羅昨天起首次訪華七天，受到高規格接待。外交部發言人華春瑩昨天表示，訪問期間，習近平主席將為巴羅舉行歡迎儀式和歡迎宴會，兩國元首將舉行會談並共同出席合作文件簽字儀式。除北京外，巴羅還將赴廈門、廣州兩地訪問。她說，中方願同岡方一道，以此訪為契機，進一步增進政治互信，全面拓展各領域友好互利合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab96ed886e5bbda13ac1b83478487079b2fafe03","tid":1131704,"uid":130901,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"68fc0673cbbef4d73807c812d187c38633c5584f","tid":1131704,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c